  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A death due to gasoline",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After an argument between the owner of the motorcycle and the person who stole the petrol while stealing the petrol from the motorcycle, the person who stole the petrol killed the owner of the motorcycle with a sharp weapon.",
        "This unfortunate incident took place in the morning of today (25th) in Borella, Castle Vri area. The injured person died on admission to the Colombo National Hospital. A 40-year-old resident of Castle Street has died.",
        "The murder was committed by a 29-year-old resident of Castle Street and he has been arrested by the police."
      ],
